column1: This year I'm thankful for the Iowans – our front line medical workers teachers first responders nursing home staffs military servicemembers & so many others – who've worked around the clock to keep us safe & help us through this difficult time.   Happy Thanksgiving #IA03. https://t.co/P8fEnQUGZb

Hundreds of thousands of Iowans lack access to the food they need to stay healthy and well-fed.  This Thanksgiving consider donating to the Food Bank of Iowa or another local food bank to help others through these difficult times. #IA03  https://t.co/1SvKbeWyxS
The callous disregard for health and human life that is alleged in this lawsuit is abhorrent.  Iowans deserve better. https://t.co/b8WGQ07MaU
